        <content type="html" xml:base="https://aw2.help/builds/power-reaper/">&lt;h1 id=&quot;overview&quot;&gt;Overview&lt;&#x2F;h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Classic power reaper spin to win playstyle. Generally speaking, this plays like:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Step 1: Prep (with abilities&#x2F;wells)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Step 2: Spin&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Step 3: Repeat&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&quot;gearing&quot;&gt;Gearing&lt;&#x2F;h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This plays quite tanky and comfy. There are some modifications below to adjust.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;hr&#x2F;&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
